---
// 探索→計画→実装→コミット — Planモードと通常モードのフロー図
---

<figure class="planmode" aria-label="PlanモードとPlanモードのフロー図">
  <div class="planmode__inner">
    <span class="planmode__title-label">探索 → 計画 → 実装 → コミット</span>

    <div class="planmode__flow">
      <!-- Plan mode -->
      <div class="planmode__phase planmode__phase--plan">
        <span class="planmode__phase-label">Plan モード</span>
        <div class="planmode__steps">
          <div class="planmode__step">探索</div>
          <div class="planmode__step-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>
          <div class="planmode__step">計画</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Approval bridge -->
      <div class="planmode__bridge" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="planmode__bridge-label">承認</span>
        <span class="planmode__bridge-arrow">→</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Normal mode -->
      <div class="planmode__phase planmode__phase--normal">
        <span class="planmode__phase-label">通常モード</span>
        <div class="planmode__steps">
          <div class="planmode__step">実装</div>
          <div class="planmode__step-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</div>
          <div class="planmode__step">コミット</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="planmode__hint">
      <span class="planmode__hint-key">Shift + Tab</span>
      <span class="planmode__hint-desc">でモードを切り替える</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="planmode__caption">
    「diffを1文で説明できる変更」は直接実行でよい。複数ファイルにまたがる変更やアプローチが不確実なときにPlanモードを使う。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .planmode {
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, white),
      var(--surface)
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .planmode__inner {
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .planmode__title-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .planmode__flow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 28rem;
  }

  .planmode__phase {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--bg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .planmode__phase--plan {
    border-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 35%, var(--border));
  }

  .planmode__phase-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-block-end: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 70%, transparent);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .planmode__phase--plan .planmode__phase-label {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 60%, transparent);
    border-color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 25%, transparent);
  }

  .planmode__steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
    gap: 0.1rem;
  }

  .planmode__step {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .planmode__step-arrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .planmode__bridge {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding-inline: 0.75rem;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .planmode__bridge-label {
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .planmode__bridge-arrow {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent-dim);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .planmode__hint {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .planmode__hint-key {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 60%, var(--bg));
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 25%, transparent);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .planmode__hint-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .planmode__caption {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-block-start: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .planmode__inner {
      padding: 1.25rem 1rem 1rem;
    }

    .planmode__flow {
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .planmode__bridge {
      flex-direction: row;
      padding-inline: 0.4rem;
    }

    .planmode__bridge-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  }
</style>
